  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为L++的蓝图差异与合并功能设计一个状态机。核心场景是用户加载左右两个蓝图版本，然后执行对比和合并操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "left_loaded",
        "ready",
        "diffing",
        "merging"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那么初始状态应该是idle，用户需要先加载左侧蓝图才能进入left_loaded状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "idle",
        "left_loaded",
        "LOAD_LEFT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，LOAD_LEFT事件触发从idle到left_loaded的转换。之后用户加载右侧蓝图，通过LOAD_RIGHT进入ready状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "left_loaded",
        "ready",
        "LOAD_RIGHT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ready状态应该支持重新加载任意一侧吧？比如用户想换一组蓝图对比。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ready",
        "LOAD_LEFT",
        "LOAD_RIGHT",
        "LOAD_BASE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，ready状态要有自循环：LOAD_LEFT、LOAD_RIGHT，还有LOAD_BASE用于加载基准版本。这三个事件都保持在ready。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ready",
        "LOAD_BASE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ready状态的自循环我记下了。那对比功能怎么触发？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ready",
        "diffing",
        "DIFF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用户执行DIFF命令时进入diffing状态，前提是blueprint_left不为空。对比完成后通过DIFF_DONE到达diff_complete状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "diffing",
        "diff_complete",
        "DIFF_DONE",
        "blueprint_left"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
