      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "还有个DIFF_ALL命令，我记得是直接跳过diffing过程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ready",
        "diff_complete",
        "DIFF_ALL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，DIFF_ALL从ready直接到diff_complete，适合批量对比场景，同样需要blueprint_left存在。",
