    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，三种视图都是自循环：SHOW_SUMMARY显示摘要，SHOW_UNIFIED显示统一格式，SHOW_PATCH显示补丁格式。都需要diff_result存在。",
      "elements_involved": [
